<font face="Verdana" size="4" color="#0000FF">Automata based formulation: 
Definitions</font> <a href="p5.htm">
<img border="0" src="next.gif" width="26" height="26"></a></p>

<div v:shape="_x0000_s1026">
  <div class="O" style="mso-line-spacing:&quot;90 30 0&quot;;mso-margin-left-alt:348">
    <p>
    &nbsp;</div>
</div>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="font-family: Verdana"><font size="5" color="#FF0000">&nbsp;A 
Chronobot</font></span><font size="5" color="#FF0000"> is a 8-tuple (M, S, f, k, s<sub>0</sub>, 
F, DB, <font face="Times New Roman">&#934;</font>)</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5">Where</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5">&nbsp;</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5"><i>M</i> is a non-empty set of 
messages (the message space)</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5">&nbsp;</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5"><i>S</i> is a non-empty set of 
states (the state space), <i>S = S<sub>c</sub> * D<sub>s</sub> * D<sub>a</sub></i></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5"><i><sub>&nbsp;</sub></i></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5">Where</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5">&nbsp;</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:1.0in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5"><i>S<sub>c </sub></i>is a 
nonempty set &nbsp;of states of the Chronobot</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </font>
</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:1.0in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5">D<i><sub>s </sub></i>is a 
nonempty set of self-models of the Chronobot, and</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5">&nbsp;</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:1.0in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5"><i>D<sub>a </sub></i>is a 
nonempty set of alien-models of the Chronobot</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5">&nbsp;</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5"><i>f : </i>&nbsp;<i>S<sub>c</sub></i> 
* (<i>M * M</i>)<sup>*</sup> <i>-&gt; S<sub>c</sub> </i>is the state transition 
function. Given the current state of the Chronobot and the history of messages 
exchanged between the Chronobot initiating the bid and the Chronobots 
participating in the bidding process, <i>f </i>specifies the next state</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph">
<font face="Verdana" size="5">&nbsp;</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><i><font face="Verdana" size="5">k</font></i><font face="Verdana" size="5"><i> : </i>&nbsp;D<i><sub>s 
* </sub>&nbsp;</i>D<i><sub>a </sub>-&gt; </i>N<sub><i> </i> </sub>is the knowledge 
distance 
function. Given the self-model of the Chronobot </font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5">and the set of all other alien 
models of Chronobots 
participating in the bidding process, <i>k</i></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5">specifies the knowledge distance 
between the negotiating entities</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Times New Roman" size="5">&#934; </font><font face="Verdana" size="5">: &nbsp;D<i><sub>s 
* </sub>&nbsp;</i>D<i><sub>a </sub>-&gt; </i>D<sub><i>s </i> </sub>is the knowledge 
plane 
function. Given the self-model of the Chronobot </font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5">and the set of all other alien 
models of Chronobots 
participating in the bidding process, </font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5">when <i>k, </i>the knowledge 
distance between the negotiating entities exceeds threshold <i>t, </i></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5">the knowledge plane function is 
responsible for transferring to the higher plane of</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5">knowledge</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5"><i>s<sub>0</sub></i> in S is the 
initial state of the&nbsp;Chronobot</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5"><b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </b></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5">F, a subset of S, is the nonempty 
set of final states</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph"><font face="Verdana" size="5">DB is the Database that stores 
the history of all the Chronobots involved in the Time/Knowledge Exchange</font></p>

